OL,3,CReport links 'illegal drugs market' to
OL,4,Cincrease in violence in prison
OL,6,FAn inspection has linked a "thriving
OL,7,Fillicit drugs market" to a rise in
OL,8,Fviolence in HMP Durham.
OL,10,FA report by HM Inspectorate of Prisons
OL,11,Ffound that most prisoners spent 22
OL,12,Fhours or more in their cells forcing
OL,13,Fthem to choose between having a
OL,14,Fshower, collecting medication or
OL,15,Fgetting fresh air. Almost all
OL,16,Fprisoners were found to be living in
OL,17,Fovercrowded conditions.
