OL,6,FPAVA incapacitating spray was also
OL,7,Fused more than any reception prison
OL,8,Fand used even when other options were
OL,9,Favailable.
OL,11,FHowever, it also found that a new
OL,12,Fgovernor and deputy had brought
OL,13,Fincreased stability to the prison that
OL,14,Fhad not been in place before leaving
OL,15,F"optimism for the future."
OL,17,FThe unannounced inspection took place
OL,18,Fin the prison between 30 April and 16
OL,19,FMay this year and assessed changes
OL,20,Fmade since the last inspection in 2021.
