OL,6,FRepresentatives from HM Inspectorate
OL,7,Fof Prisons questioned prisoners, staff
OL,8,Fand helpers as well as consulting
OL,9,Fprison documents.
OL,11,FThey found the time prisoners spent in
OL,12,Ftheir cells to be the "most worrying
OL,13,Faspect" of the inspection and
OL,14,Fsomething that had led to the
OL,15,Fextensive use of illegal drugs and the
OL,16,Fincrease in violence.
OL,18,FOther findings included:
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
