OL,6,FHowever, HM Chief Inspector of Prisons
OL,7,FCharlie Taylor said there was
OL,8,F"cautious optimism" for the future
OL,9,Fafter a difficult 18 months.
OL,11,FThe inspection found that positive
OL,12,Fsteps were being made by the new
OL,13,FGovernor and leadership team to
OL,14,Fimprove reception processes and
OL,15,Fprovide more meaningful activity for
OL,16,Fprisoners.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
