OL,6,FOne of the most positive aspects of
OL,7,Fthe prison was a good relationship
OL,8,Fbetween prisoners and officers. The
OL,9,Fsegregation unit was also well managed
OL,10,Fand better led than the last
OL,11,Finspection while staff were said to
OL,12,Fhave coped well with changing
OL,13,Ftimescales of early release schemes.
OL,15,FPrison management will now have to
OL,16,Faddress the concerns and set out a
OL,17,Fplan for them to be resolved,
OL,18,Fincluding the prison inspectorate in
OL,19,Fthe process.
