OL,6,FIn response to the report's findings,
OL,7,Fa spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice said: "This government is
OL,9,Fcommitted to creating better citizens,
OL,10,Fnot criminals, and the findings in
OL,11,Fthis report are exactly why we are
OL,12,Fgripping the situation in prisons and
OL,13,Fsupporting our hardworking staff.
OL,15,F"HMP Durham has already taken swift
OL,16,Faction to address the concerns
OL,17,Fincluding a full refurbishment of
OL,18,Fcells and is clamping down on illicit
OL,19,Fitems by using its airport-style
OL,20,Fscanner to detect and thwart items
OL,21,Ffrom entering the prison."
